<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>My Bond Forever</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Love, how I need to feel your love
 What has changed me is your love
 My whole strength is in your love
 Love is what I want to live
 It scares every fear, and sets me free
 Be love my way, my bond forever

[V2]
 Love, even through my darkest pain
 I won't let you fade away
 I'll remember

[V3]
 I know I know I know I know
 You gave your life for me
 I know I know I know I know
 You carried on your shoulders all my sins
 I know I know I know I know
 (You saved me)
 You saved me

[V4]
 This left no doubt that you love me
 I won't fear what man shall do to me
 God, you're my first and greatest love
 Love is what I want to live
 It scares every fear, and sets me free
 Be love my way, my bond forever

[V5]
 I know I know I know I know
 You gave your life for me
 I know I know I know I know
 You carried on your shoulders all my sins
 I know I know I know I know
 (You saved me)
 You saved me</lyrics>
